a motorbike delivering it and what not.

320
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:59,420
But if she is the criminal, then everything does make sense.

321
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:01,500
Then...

322
00:18:02,570 --> 00:18:04,300
M-Me?

323
00:18:04,870 --> 00:18:08,210
Hinagiku-san, we never thought you'd be the criminal.

324
00:18:08,210 --> 00:18:10,420
But it was so convincing.

325
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:13,030
Yes. She's the least suspicious of us.

326
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:14,310
Therefore she becomes suspicious.

327
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:15,440
Yeah, yeah.

328
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:21,840
That was a wonderful deduction.

329
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:24,330
I never thought you'd figure it out.

330
00:18:24,330 --> 00:18:25,450
Yes, she's right.

331
00:18:25,450 --> 00:18:27,840
I am the criminal.

332
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:29,010
No, that's wrong.

333
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:32,080
The criminal is not Hinagiku.

334
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:34,820
Hey, don't take my scene away!

335
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:37,210
You surprised me so much, the anesthesia burned out in me.

336
00:18:38,170 --> 00:18:41,150
From the developments, only I can be the criminal.

337
00:18:41,150 --> 00:18:44,050
But that would make this all too simple and boring.

338
00:18:44,050 --> 00:18:48,580
Um, that's making it hard
to figure out who's speaking, so can you stop it?

339
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:52,490
You've all forgotten something!

340
00:18:52,490 --> 00:18:56,210
There is one more very suspicious person!

341
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:57,620
One more person?

342
00:18:57,620 --> 00:18:59,480
Yes! And that individual is...

343
00:18:59,940 --> 00:19:01,090
That individual is?

344
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:07,560
The person doing the voice in the sky!

345
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:09,220
Me?

346
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:12,890
Milady, isn't that getting too absurd?

347
00:19:12,890 --> 00:19:14,100
No, this is good.

348
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:18,140
But I don't think the viewers will accept it.

349
00:19:18,140 --> 00:19:21,650
It's a suspense story produced and enacted by me.

350
00:19:21,650 --> 00:19:24,110
I won't let anyone complain.

351
00:19:24,110 --> 00:19:25,140
Hey!

352
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:28,440
